  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Wind Charm</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/32px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n<span class=\"box headnote\"><i>This content is available only after activating the</i> <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lunar_Rift\" title=\"Lunar Rift\"><img alt=\"Map Icon Lunar Rift.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Map_Icon_Lunar_Rift.png/28px-Map_Icon_Lunar_Rift.png?34c0a1\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\"></a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lunar_Rift\" title=\"Lunar Rift\">Lunar Rift</a></i></span><br>\n</p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><b>Wind Charms</b> are decoration items that can be hung on the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hermit_Home\" title=\"Hermit Home\">Hermit Home</a> and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Winter%27s_Feast_Tree\" title=\"Winter&#x27;s Feast Tree\">Winter&#x27;s Feast Tree</a>. They can be crafted near <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pearl\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Pearl\">Pearl</a> after upgrading <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hermit_Home\" title=\"Hermit Home\">Hermit Home</a> to the 5th level. There are 7 variations of Wind Charms. During <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Winter%27s_Feast\" title=\"Winter&#x27;s Feast\">Winter&#x27;s Feast</a>, 4 more variations are available: A Snowflake, Bow, Stocking, and Wreath.\n</p><p>The Wind Charms can also be traded to the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pig_King/DST\" title=\"Pig King/DST\">Pig King</a> for 3 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Gold_Nugget/DST\" title=\"Gold Nugget/DST\">Gold Nuggets</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Skins\"><img alt=\"Voidbag Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Voidbag_Icon.png/32px-Voidbag_Icon.png?3b640b\" width=\"32\" height=\"33\"> Skins</span></h2>\n<p><span class=\"box headnote\"><i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Glommer%27s_Flower.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Glommer&#x27;s Flower.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Glommer%27s_Flower.png/25px-Glommer%27s_Flower.png?22167d\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\"></a> Main article:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Belongings#Records\" title=\"Belongings\">Belongings</a></span><br>\n</p>\n<ul><li>The <b><span class=\"skin-rarity-complimentary\">Complimentary</span></b> skins are available to all players initially.</li>\n<li>The <b><span class=\"skin-rarity-event\">Event</span></b> skins does not drop normally. Instead, it is usable by everyone during the official <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Winter%27s_Feast\" title=\"Winter&#x27;s Feast\">Winter&#x27;s Feast</a> event.</li></ul>\n<div>\n<div class=\"skin-info\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Wind_Charm_Wood.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Wind Charm Wood.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Wind_Charm_Wood.png?c3b385\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"></a></div><div><span class=\"skin-rarity-complimentary\"><b>Complimentary</b></span></div><div class=\"skin-name\"><b>Wood</b></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"skin-info\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Wind_Charm_Salt_Crystal.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Wind Charm Salt Crystal.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Wind_Charm_Salt_Crystal.png?4bf42b\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"></a></div><div><span class=\"skin-rarity-complimentary\"><b>Complimentary</b></span></div><div class=\"skin-name\"><b>Salt Crystal</b></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"skin-info\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Wind_Charm_Sand_Dollar.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Wind Charm Sand Dollar.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Wind_Charm_Sand_Dollar.png?e074bd\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"></a></div><div><span class=\"skin-rarity-complimentary\"><b>Complimentary</b></span></div><div class=\"skin-name\"><b>Sand Dollar</b></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"skin-info\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Wind_Charm_Coral.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Wind Charm Coral.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Wind_Charm_Coral.png?7d50c7\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"></a></div><div><span class=\"skin-rarity-complimentary\"><b>Complimentary</b></span></div><div class=\"skin-name\"><b>Coral</b></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"skin-info\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Wind_Charm_Driftwood.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Wind Charm Driftwood.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Wind_Charm_Driftwood.png?9c5aa0\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"></a></div><div><span class=\"skin-rarity-complimentary\"><b>Complimentary</b></span></div><div class=\"skin-name\"><b>Driftwood</b></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"skin-info\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Wind_Charm_Mushroom.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Wind Charm Mushroom.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Wind_Charm_Mushroom.png?d0498c\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"></a></div><div><span class=\"skin-rarity-complimentary\"><b>Complimentary</b></span></div><div class=\"skin-name\"><b>Mushroom</b></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"skin-info\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Wind_Charm_Snowflake.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Wind Charm Snowflake.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Wind_Charm_Snowflake.png?bd8b60\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"></a></div><div><span class=\"skin-rarity-event\"><b>Event</b></span></div><div class=\"skin-name\"><b>Snowflake</b></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"skin-info\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Wind_Charm_Bow.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Wind Charm Bow.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Wind_Charm_Bow.png?309d4c\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"></a></div><div><span class=\"skin-rarity-event\"><b>Event</b></span></div><div class=\"skin-name\"><b>Bow</b></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"skin-info\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Wind_Charm_Stocking.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Wind Charm Stocking.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Wind_Charm_Stocking.png?a60c7e\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"></a></div><div><span class=\"skin-rarity-event\"><b>Event</b></span></div><div class=\"skin-name\"><b>Stocking</b></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"skin-info\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Wind_Charm_Wreath.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Wind Charm Wreath.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Wind_Charm_Wreath.png?c7c9c1\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"></a></div><div><span class=\"skin-rarity-event\"><b>Event</b></span></div><div class=\"skin-name\"><b>Wreath</b></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Assets\"><img alt=\"Research Notes.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Research_Notes.png/32px-Research_Notes.png?ef2da4\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"> Assets</span></h2>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Shell-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wind_Charm#Shell-0\">Shell</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Wood-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wind_Charm#Wood-0\">Wood</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Salt_Crystal-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wind_Charm#Salt_Crystal-0\">Salt Crystal</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Sand_Dollar-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wind_Charm#Sand_Dollar-0\">Sand Dollar</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Coral-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wind_Charm#Coral-0\">Coral</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Driftwood-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wind_Charm#Driftwood-0\">Drif