  "plainText": "Wind Charm\nShell\nWood\nSalt Crystal\nSand Dollar\nCoral\nDriftwood\nMushroom\nSnowflake\nBow\nStocking\nWreath\n\"Give Pearl's Place a splash of whimsy with some oceanside adornments.\"\nShell\nWood\nSalt Crystal\nSand Dollar\nCoral\nDriftwood\nMushroom\nSnowflake\nBow\nStocking\nWreath\nObject Info\n40\nCrafting\n×1 ×1\nFilters\nTier\nMiscellaneous\n\"hermithouse_ornament\"\nExclusive to:\nThis content is available only after activating the Lunar Rift\n“How chiming.”\n–Wilson\n“But what does it do?”\n–Willow\n“Is quite elegant.”\n–Wolfgang\n“It's pleasant.”\n–Wendy\n“HATE IT”\n–WX-78\n“An attractive ornament to be hung on Pearl's house.”\n–Wickerbottom\n“That would really spruce up the old cabin.”\n–Woodie\n“Cute.”\n–Maxwell\n“By the wind's töuch, it döth dance.”\n–Wigfrid\n“Will there still be room for webs?”\n–Webber\n“How quaint!”\n–Warly\n“Pretty stuff for crabby friend house”\n–Wormwood\n“Aw, that's sweet.”\n–Winona\n“Lifts the mood of her humble abood.”\n–Wortox\n“Just for crabby lady!”\n–Wurt\n“I remember making these at camp!”\n–Walter\n“Rather charming.”\n–Wanda\nWind Charms are decoration items that can be hung on the Hermit Home and Winter's Feast Tree. They can be crafted near Pearl after upgrading Hermit Home to the 5th level. There are 7 variations of Wind Charms. During Winter's Feast, 4 more variations are available: A Snowflake, Bow, Stocking, and Wreath.\nThe Wind Charms can also be traded to the Pig King for 3 Gold Nuggets.\nSkins[edit | edit source]\nMain article: Belongings\nThe Complimentary skins are available to all players initially.\nThe Event skins does not drop normally. Instead, it is usable by everyone during the official Winter's Feast event.\nComplimentary\nWood\nComplimentary\nSalt Crystal\nComplimentary\nSand Dollar\nComplimentary\nCoral\nComplimentary\nDriftwood\nComplimentary\nMushroom\nEvent\nSnowflake\nEvent\nBow\nEvent\nStocking\nEvent\nWreath\nAssets[edit | edit source]\nShellWoodSalt CrystalSand DollarCoral