harming.\n|choose = wormwood}}\n\n'''Wind Charms''' are decoration items that can be hung on the [[Hermit Home]] and [[Winter's Feast Tree]]. They can be crafted near [[Pearl]] after upgrading [[Hermit Home]] to the 5th level. There are 7 variations of Wind Charms. During [[Winter's Feast]], 4 more variations are available: A Snowflake, Bow, Stocking, and Wreath.\n\nThe Wind Charms can also be traded to the {{DSTL|Pig King}} for 3 {{DSTL|Gold Nugget}}s.\n== [[File:Skins Icon.png|32px|link=]] Skins ==\n<noinclude>{{Main|Belongings#Records|Belongings}}</noinclude>\n* The '''<span class=\"skin-rarity-complimentary\">Complimentary</span>''' skins are available to all players initially. \n* The '''<span class=\"skin-rarity-event\">Event</span>''' skins does not drop normally. Instead, it is usable by everyone during the official [[Winter's Feast]] event.\n<div style=\"display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; justify-content: center;\">\n{{SkinInfo\n|image = Wind Charm Wood.png\n|rarity = Complimentary\n|name = Wood\n}}\n{{SkinInfo\n|image = Wind Charm Salt Crystal.png\n|rarity = Complimentary\n|name = Salt Crystal\n}}\n{{SkinInfo\n|image = Wind Charm Sand Dollar.png\n|rarity = Complimentary\n|name = Sand Dollar\n}}\n{{SkinInfo\n|image = Wind Charm Coral.png\n|rarity = Complimentary\n|name = Coral\n}}\n{{SkinInfo\n|image = Wind Charm Driftwood.png\n|rarity = Complimentary\n|name = Driftwood\n}}\n{{SkinInfo\n|image = Wind Charm Mushroom.png\n|rarity = Complimentary\n|name = Mushroom\n}}\n{{SkinInfo\n|image = Wind Charm Snowflake.png\n|rarity = Event\n|name = Snowflake\n}}\n{{SkinInfo\n|image = Wind Charm Bow.png\n|rarity = Event\n|name = Bow\n}}\n{{SkinInfo\n|image = Wind Charm Stocking.png\n|rarity = Event\n|name = Stocking\n}}\n{{SkinInfo\n|image = Wind Charm Wreath.png\n|rarity = Event\n|name = Wreath\n}}\n</div>\n\n{{clear}}\n\n== [[File:Research Notes.png|32px|link=]] Assets ==\n<tabber>\n|-| Shell =\n<gallery>\nWind Charm Hanged.png|Hanged\nWind Charm Hanged Place.g